=== Research Group

[group.html ROMA Lab] is looking for highly self-motivated Ph.D. students, working on optimization algorithms for machine learning problems, statistical machine learning, conformal prediction and risk-aware robust learning. If you share similar research interests in machine learning, please send your CV and research proposal (if any) to yan.yan1 AT wsu DOT edu. Due to the large number of emails we receive, we cannot respond to every email individually. Thanks!


